      "author": "MarsLuay",
      "description": "## Changes\n- Fixed lint/static-analysis warnings around popout-safe DOM/timer use, unsafe font attribute reads, unnecessary assertions, deprecated APIs, and command IDs.\n- Removed stylesheet `!important` usage and tightened the theme CSS guard so future uses fail.\n- Added issue/PR templates plus code of conduct and security policy metadata.\n- Kept `pptx-svg` pinned at `0.5.10`; `0.6.2` failed highlight/run-property regression tests during verification.\n\n## Verification\n- `npm run build`\n- `npm run lint`\n- `npm test` (216/216)\n- `node --test scripts/smoke-native-powerpoint-doc-editor-load.cjs`\n- `scripts/code-analysis/run-code-analysis.mjs /tmp/native-powerpoint-doc-editor-push` (45/45 pass)",
